\begin_layout Subsection
Lecture 3: Compensated Compactness
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
非线性或线性PDEs的一个本质上的难点: 弱收敛之积不再保持弱收敛.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
在第一讲中, 有结论: 
\begin_inset Formula $A\left(\frac{x}{\varepsilon}\right)\nabla u^{\varepsilon}\wc A^{\circ}\nabla u^{\circ}$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $L^{2}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

.
 其中, 
\begin_inset Formula $A^{\circ}=\bar{A}+\bar{A\nabla\chi}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $A^{\circ}$
\end_inset

通常与
\begin_inset Formula $A\left(\frac{x}{\varepsilon}\right)$
\end_inset

的弱极限
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{A}$
\end_inset

不同.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
以下证明, 在导数的某种线性组合下有界的条件下, 积的弱极限等于弱极限之积.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $\Omega$
\end_inset

: 
\begin_inset Formula $\RR^{d}$
\end_inset

中有界Lipschitz区域.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $v_{n}=v_{n}\left(x\right)\in\RR^{d}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $w_{n}=w_{n}\left(x\right)\in\RR^{d}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $v_{n}$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $H^{1}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

中有界, 
\begin_inset Formula $v_{n}\wc v$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $L^{2}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $w_{n}$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $L^{2}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

中有界, 
\begin_inset Formula $w_{n}\wc w$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $L^{2}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Rellich紧嵌入定理推出, 有子列
\begin_inset Formula $v_{n}\to v$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $L^{2}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

, 故
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v_{n}\cdot w_{n}\wc v\cdot w\ \ \text{ in }\ L^{1}\left(\Omega\right).
\]

\end_inset

从而整个序列收敛.
 这在Navier-Stokes方程中的非线性项取极限时遇到, 在那里
\begin_inset Formula $u_{n}$
\end_inset

由一列光滑序列逼近.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
核心: div-curl引理.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Note Note
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
TODO
\end_layout

\end_inset

Newtonian potential
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
div-curl引理: 
\begin_inset Formula $v\in D'\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $v=v\left(x\right)\in\RR^{d}$
\end_inset

, 定义
\begin_inset Formula $\text{div}v=\text{div}v\left(x\right)\in\RR$
\end_inset

.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\text{div}v:=\p_{x_{\alpha}}v_{\alpha}$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $D'\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $w\in D'\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $w=w\left(x\right)\in\RR^{d}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\curl w=\curl w\left(x\right)\in\RR^{d^{2}}$
\end_inset

.
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\curl w\right)_{\alpha\beta}:=\p_{x_{\beta}}w^{\alpha}-\p_{x_{\alpha}}w^{\beta}\ \text{ in }\ D'\left(\Omega\right),\quad1\le\alpha,\beta\le d.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
试证: 若
\begin_inset Formula $v\in D'\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $D^{\alpha}v\in D'\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\forall\alpha\in\NN^{d}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
(Div-Curl lemma) 
\begin_inset Formula $1<p<\infty$
\end_inset

.
 
\begin_inset Formula $v_{n}=v_{n}\left(x\right)\in L^{p}\left(\Omega;\RR^{d}\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathrm{div}v_{n}\in L^{p}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $w_{n}=w_{n}\left(x\right)\in L^{p'}\left(\Omega;\RR^{d}\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathrm{curl}w_{n}\in L^{p'}\left(\Omega;\RR^{d^{2}}\right)$
\end_inset

.
 假设:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset Formula $\norm{v_{n}}_{L^{p}\left(\Omega\right)}+\norm{\mathrm{div}v_{n}}_{L^{p}\left(\Omega\right)}$
\end_inset

一致有界, 
\begin_inset Formula $v_{n}\wc v$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $L^{p}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset Formula $\norm{w_{n}}_{L^{p'}\left(\Omega\right)}+\norm{\mathrm{curl}w_{n}}_{L^{p'}\left(\Omega\right)}$
\end_inset

一致有界, 
\begin_inset Formula $w_{n}\wc w$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $L^{p'}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
则
\begin_inset Formula $v_{n}\cdot w_{n}\wc v\cdot w$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $D'$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在div-curl引理中, 我们只对导数的线性组合进行控制, 而Rellich紧性定理却要对
\begin_inset Formula $v_{n}$
\end_inset

或
\begin_inset Formula $w_{n}$
\end_inset

的所有一阶导数有控制.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
div-curl引理常用于满足
\begin_inset Formula $\mathrm{div}v_{n}=0$
\end_inset

或
\begin_inset Formula $\mathrm{curl}w_{n}=0$
\end_inset

的序列.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
\begin_inset Formula $p=p'=2$
\end_inset

时, 用Fourier变换的直接证明, 证明中对于任意的有界区域
\begin_inset Formula $\Omega$
\end_inset

适用, 而不需对
\begin_inset Formula $\partial\Omega$
\end_inset

做更多的假设.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
The strategy: 低频, 高频部分与Rellich's injection 
\begin_inset Formula $H_{0}^{1}\left(\Omega\right)\Subset L^{2}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

对比.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
\begin_inset Formula $\forall\varphi\in C_{c}^{\infty}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\psi\in C_{c}^{\infty}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\psi\vert_{\mathrm{spt}\varphi}=1$
\end_inset

.
 定义
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\widetilde{v_{n}}:=\begin{cases}
\varphi v_{n} & \text{in }\Omega\\
0 & \text{on }\partial\Omega
\end{cases},\qquad\widetilde{w_{n}}:=\begin{cases}
\psi w_{n} & \text{in }\Omega\\
0 & \text{on }\partial\Omega
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset

则有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{\Omega}v_{n}\cdot w_{n}\varphi=\int_{\RR^{d}}\widetilde{v_{n}}\cdot\widetilde{w_{n}}=\int_{\RR^{d}}\widehat{\widetilde{v_{n}}}\cdot\widehat{\widetilde{w_{n}}}.
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\widehat{\widetilde{v_{n}}},\widehat{\widetilde{w_{n}}}$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $L^{2}\left(\RR^{d}\right)$
\end_inset

中有界.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\widehat{\widetilde{v_{n}}}\wc\widehat{\widetilde{v}}$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $L^{2}\left(\RR^{d}\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\widehat{\widetilde{w_{n}}}\wc\widehat{\widetilde{w}}$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $L^{2}\left(\RR^{d}\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\xi_{\alpha}\widehat{\widetilde{v_{n,\alpha}}}$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $L^{2}\left(\RR^{d}\right)$
\end_inset

中有界.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\xi_{\beta}\widehat{\widetilde{w_{n,\alpha}}}-\xi_{\alpha}\widehat{\widetilde{w_{n,\beta}}}$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $L^{2}\left(\RR^{d}\right)$
\end_inset

中有界.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{\RR^{d}}\widehat{\widetilde{v_{n}}}\cdot\widehat{\widetilde{w_{n}}}=\int_{B\left(0,R\right)}\widehat{\widetilde{v_{n}}}\cdot\widehat{\widetilde{w_{n}}}+\int_{\RR^{d}\setminus B\left(0,R\right)}\widehat{\widetilde{v_{n}}}\cdot\widehat{\widetilde{w_{n}}},\qquad R>0.
\]

\end_inset

低频: 
\begin_inset Formula $\norm{\widehat{\widetilde{v_{n}}}}_{L^{\infty}\left(\RR^{d}\right)}\le\norm{\widetilde{v}}_{L^{1}\left(\Omega\right)}\le C_{\Omega}\norm{v_{n}}_{L^{2}}$
\end_inset

, 同理
\begin_inset Formula $\norm{\widehat{\widetilde{w_{n}}}}_{\infty}\lesssim\norm{w_{n}}_{2}$
\end_inset

.
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\widehat{\widetilde{v_{n}}}\left(\xi\right)=\int_{\Omega}\widetilde{v_{n}}\ue^{-\ui x\cdot\xi}\ud x\to\int_{\Omega}\widetilde{v}\ue^{-\ui x\cdot\xi}\ud x=\widehat{\widetilde{v}}\left(\xi\right)
\]

\end_inset

即有点态收敛, 同理
\begin_inset Formula $\widehat{\widetilde{w_{n}}}\to\widehat{\widetilde{w}}$
\end_inset

 a.e., 所以DCT可得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{B\left(0,R\right)}\widehat{\widetilde{v_{n}}}\cdot\widehat{\widetilde{w_{n}}}\to\int_{B\left(0,R\right)}\widehat{\widetilde{v}}\cdot\widehat{\widetilde{w}}.
\]

\end_inset

高频: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left|\int_{\RR^{d}\setminus B\left(0,R\right)}\widehat{\widetilde{v_{n}}}\cdot\widehat{\widetilde{w_{n}}}\right|=\left|\int_{\RR^{d}\setminus B\left(0,R\right)}\frac{\xi^{\beta}\cdot\xi^{\beta}}{\left|\xi\right|^{2}}\widehat{\widetilde{v_{n}}}\cdot\widehat{\widetilde{w_{n}}}\right|\le\frac{1}{R}\int_{\RR^{d}\setminus B\left(0,R\right)}\left|\xi^{\beta}\widehat{\widetilde{v_{n}}}^{\alpha}\widehat{\widetilde{w_{n}}}^{\alpha}\right|\le\frac{1}{R}\int_{\RR^{d}\setminus B\left(0,R\right)}\left|\xi^{\alpha}\widehat{\widetilde{v_{n}}}^{\alpha}\widehat{\widetilde{w_{n}}}^{\beta}\right|+\left|\left(\xi^{\beta}\widehat{\widetilde{w_{n}}}^{\alpha}-\xi^{\alpha}\widehat{\widetilde{w_{n}}}^{\beta}\right)\widehat{\widetilde{v_{n}}}^{\alpha}\right|=O\left(\frac{1}{R}\right).
\]

\end_inset

所以
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{\Omega}v_{n}\cdot w_{n}\varphi\to\int_{B\left(0,R\right)}\widehat{\widetilde{v}}\cdot\widehat{\widetilde{w}}+O\left(\frac{1}{R}\right),\qquad n\to\infty.
\]

\end_inset

所以
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{\Omega}v_{n}\cdot w_{n}\varphi\to\int_{\RR^{d}}\widehat{\widetilde{v}}\cdot\widehat{\widetilde{w}}=\int_{\RR^{d}}\widetilde{v}\cdot\widetilde{w}=\int_{\Omega}v\cdot w\varphi.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $1<p,p'<\infty$
\end_inset

时
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
此时Fourier变换不再适用.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
当存在序列
\begin_inset Formula $z_{n}$
\end_inset

使得
\begin_inset Formula $w_{n}=\nabla z_{n}$
\end_inset

且
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{cases}
z_{n}\to z & \text{ in }L^{p'}\left(\Omega\right)\\
\nabla z_{n}\wc\nabla z & \text{ in }L^{p'}\left(\Omega\right)
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset

所以有
\begin_inset Formula $\mathrm{curl}w_{n}=0$
\end_inset

.
 所以
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{\Omega}v_{n}\cdot w_{n}\varphi=\int_{\Omega}v_{n}\cdot\nabla z_{n}\varphi=-\int_{\Omega}\mathrm{div}v_{n}\cdot z_{n}\varphi-\int_{\Omega}\left(v_{n}\cdot\nabla\varphi\right)z_{n}\to-\int_{\Omega}\mathrm{div}v\cdot z\varphi-\int_{\Omega}\left(v\cdot\nabla\varphi\right)z=\int_{\Omega}\left(v\cdot\nabla z\right)\varphi=\int_{\Omega}v\cdot w\varphi.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
A few singular integrals
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $-\Delta$
\end_inset

的基本解:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Gamma\left(x\right):=\begin{cases}
\frac{1}{2\pi}\log\left|x\right| & d=2\\
c_{d}\frac{1}{\left|x\right|^{d-2}} & d\ge3.
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\forall f\in C_{0}^{\infty}\left(\RR^{d}\right)$
\end_inset

, 牛顿位势
\begin_inset Formula $u\left(x\right)=\Gamma*f\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $-\Delta u=f$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $x\in\RR^{d}$
\end_inset

的弱解.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proposition
如下结论成立
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
设
\begin_inset Formula $1<q<d$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $\exists c>0$
\end_inset

使得
\begin_inset Formula $\forall f\in L^{q}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

, 牛顿位势
\begin_inset Formula $u=\Gamma*f$
\end_inset

满足
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\norm{\nabla u}_{L^{q^{*}}\left(\Omega\right)}\le C\norm{f}_{q;\Omega}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
设
\begin_inset Formula $1<q<\infty$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $\exists c>0$
\end_inset

使得
\begin_inset Formula $\forall f\in L^{q}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

, 牛顿位势
\begin_inset Formula $u=\Gamma*f$
\end_inset

满足
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\norm{\nabla^{2}u}_{q;\Omega}\le C\norm{f}_{q;\Omega}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
关于
\begin_inset Formula $\nabla u$
\end_inset

的估计, 可由以下形式的奇异积分得到:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对于
\begin_inset Formula $0<\alpha<d$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $f\in C_{c}^{\infty}\left(\RR^{d}\right)$
\end_inset

, define:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
I_{\alpha}f\left(x\right):=\frac{1}{\left|\cdot\right|^{d-\alpha}}*f\left(x\right)=\int_{\RR^{d}}\frac{1}{\left|x-y\right|^{d-\alpha}}f\left(y\right)\ud y.
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\nabla\Gamma\left(x\right)=\begin{cases}
\frac{1}{2\pi}\frac{x}{\left|x\right|^{2}} & d=2\\
c_{d}\left(2-d\right)\frac{x}{\left|x\right|^{d}} & d\ge3.
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Proposition
\begin_inset Formula $\forall0<\alpha<d$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\forall1<p<\frac{d}{\alpha}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\forall f\in L^{p}\left(\RR^{d}\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\norm{I_{\alpha}f}_{q;\RR^{d}}\le C\norm{f}_{p;\RR^{d}},
\]

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{q}=\frac{1}{p}-\frac{\alpha}{d}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $C=C\left(\alpha,d,p\right)$
\end_inset

, say 
\begin_inset Formula $I_{\alpha}$
\end_inset

 is (强) 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(p,q\right)$
\end_inset

型算子.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Note Note
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
TODO
\end_layout

\end_inset

convolution in Lorentz spaces.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Remark, 通过缩放, 可以求出
\begin_inset Formula $q$
\end_inset

是满足以上表达式的.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
以上命题可以推出, 当
\begin_inset Formula $1<p<d$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{p^{*}}=\frac{1}{p}-\frac{1}{d}$
\end_inset

时, 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\norm{\nabla u}_{p^{*};\RR^{d}}\le C\norm{I_{1}f}_{p^{*};\RR^{d}}\le C\norm{f}_{p;\RR^{d}}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对
\begin_inset Formula $\nabla^{2}u$
\end_inset

的估计, 对于
\begin_inset Formula $d\ge2$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $1\le\alpha,\beta\le d$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\partial_{x_{\alpha}}\partial_{x_{\beta}}\Gamma\left(x\right)=\begin{cases}
-d\frac{\widetilde{c_{d}}}{\left|x\right|^{\alpha}}\cdot\frac{x_{\alpha}x_{\beta}}{\left|x\right|^{2}}, & \alpha\ne\beta\\
\frac{\widetilde{c_{d}}}{\left|x\right|^{d}}\left\{ 1-d\frac{x_{\alpha}^{2}}{\left|x\right|^{2}}\right\} , & \alpha=\beta.
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset

当
\begin_inset Formula $d=2$
\end_inset

时, 
\begin_inset Formula $\widetilde{c_{2}}=\frac{1}{2\pi}$
\end_inset

, 当
\begin_inset Formula $d\ge3$
\end_inset

时, 
\begin_inset Formula $\widetilde{c_{d}}=\left(2-d\right)c_{d}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
求导之后的核在
\begin_inset Formula $0$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\infty$
\end_inset

附近不再可积, 在上面的命题中相当于
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha=0$
\end_inset

, 这样不能再用以上命题了.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在某些情况下, subtle cancellations properties可以定义一个算子并证其有界性, 如在Calderon-Zygmund理论便是如此处
理的.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proposition
定义自
\begin_inset Formula $f\in C_{0}^{\infty}\left(\RR^{d}\right)$
\end_inset

上的算子
\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

: 
\begin_inset Formula $Tf\left(x\right):=p.v.\ K*f\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

, 对于任何
\begin_inset Formula $p\in\left(1,\infty\right)$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $L^{p}\left(\RR^{d}\right)\to L^{p}\left(\RR^{d}\right)$
\end_inset

有界线性算子.
 其中
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
K\left(x\right):=\frac{1}{\left|x\right|^{d}}\omega\left(\frac{x}{\left|x\right|}\right),
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\omega=\omega\left(s\right)$
\end_inset

是定义在
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{S}^{d-1}$
\end_inset

上的Lipschitz函数, 使得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{\mathbb{S}^{d-1}}\omega\left(s\right)\ud\sigma\left(s\right)=0.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

