\begin_layout Standard
能量收敛: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\xi^{\varepsilon}\left(x\right):=A\left(\frac{x}{\varepsilon}\right)\nabla u^{\varepsilon}\wc A^{\circ}\nabla u^{\circ}\ \text{ in }\ L^{2}\left(\Omega\right).
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\nabla u^{\varepsilon}\wc\nabla u^{\circ}\ \text{ in }L^{2}\left(\Omega\right).
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
A^{\circ}=\overline{A}+\overline{A\nabla\chi}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\nabla\cdot\xi^{\varepsilon}=\mathrm{div}\xi^{\varepsilon}=-f.
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Longrightarrow A\left(\frac{x}{\varepsilon}\right)\nabla u^{\varepsilon}\cdot\nabla u^{\varepsilon}\wc A^{\circ}\nabla u^{\circ}\cdot\nabla u^{\circ}\ \text{ in }D'.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Jacobian行列式的弱连续性.
 证明中用到了
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{M}\left(\Omega\right)\subset\left(L^{\infty}\left(\Omega\right)\right)'$
\end_inset

, 是否有
\begin_inset Formula $\left(L^{\infty}\left(\Omega\right)\right)'\subset\mathcal{M}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
应用泛函分析, 薛小平
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
广义函数简介
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
算子演算, 对Heaviside函数求导数, 把导数记为
\begin_inset Formula $\delta\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
波函数具有形式
\begin_inset Formula $\ue^{\ui\lambda x}$
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset Formula $x\in\RR$
\end_inset

), 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda\in\RR$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Cauchy积分: 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{2\pi}\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}\ue^{\ui\lambda x}\ud x=\lim_{n\to\infty}\frac{1}{2\pi}\int_{-n}^{n}\ue^{\ui\lambda x}=\lim_{n\to\infty}\frac{1}{\pi}\frac{\sin n\lambda}{\lambda}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{\pi}\frac{\sin n\lambda}{\lambda}\wc\delta\left(x\right),\ \lambda\to\infty$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
广义微商理论.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
基本函数空间
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $C_{0}^{k}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

表示
\begin_inset Formula $C^{k}\left(\bar{\Omega}\right)$
\end_inset

中满足支集是
\begin_inset Formula $\Omega$
\end_inset

内紧集(有界闭集)的所有函数组成的空间.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
设
\begin_inset Formula $u\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $\Omega$
\end_inset

上定义的一个可积函数, 并且在
\begin_inset Formula $\Omega$
\end_inset

的一个紧集
\begin_inset Formula $K$
\end_inset

外恒为零, 则当
\begin_inset Formula $\delta>0$
\end_inset

充分小时
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u_{\delta}\left(x\right)=\int_{\Omega}u\left(y\right)j_{\delta}\left(x-y\right)\ud y
\]

\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $C_{0}^{\infty}\left(\RR^{n}\right)$
\end_inset

中的函数.
 其中
\begin_inset Formula $j_{\delta}\left(x\right)=\frac{1}{\delta^{n}}j\left(\frac{x}{\delta}\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
j\left(x\right)=\begin{cases}
C_{n}\ue^{-\frac{1}{1-\norm{x}^{2}}}, & \norm{x}<1;\\
0, & \norm{x}\ge1.
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $C_{n}$
\end_inset

是依赖于维数
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

的常数, 使
\begin_inset Formula $\int_{\norm{x}\le1}j\left(x\right)\ud x=1$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
为什么以上定理的条件要求
\begin_inset Formula $u$
\end_inset

支在紧集
\begin_inset Formula $K$
\end_inset

中?如果去掉此条件将如何?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
如果
\begin_inset Formula $u$
\end_inset

的可积性取消将如何, 比如
\begin_inset Formula $u$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $\partial K$
\end_inset

的邻域附近积分为无穷?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
设
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \varphi_{i}\right\} \subset C_{c}^{\infty}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi\in C_{c}^{\infty}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

, 如果满足下列条件:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
存在一个紧集
\begin_inset Formula $K\subset\Omega$
\end_inset

使得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\text{spt}\left(\varphi_{j}\right)\subset K(j=1,2,\cdots),\quad\text{spt}\left(\varphi\right)\subset K;
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
对于任意多重指标
\begin_inset Formula $p=\left(p_{1},p_{2},\cdots,p_{n}\right)$
\end_inset

, 函数列
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ D^{p}\varphi_{j}\right\} $
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $K$
\end_inset

上一致收敛于
\begin_inset Formula $D^{p}\varphi$
\end_inset

, 即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\max_{x\in K}\left|D^{p}\varphi_{j}\left(x\right)-D^{p}\varphi\left(x\right)\right|\to0,j\to\infty,
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
则称
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \varphi_{i}\right\} $
\end_inset

收敛于
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi$
\end_inset

, that is 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi_{j}\to\varphi$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

, 称
\begin_inset Formula $C_{c}^{\infty}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

按照收敛概念及线性运算为基本函数空间, 并记为
\begin_inset Formula $D\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{D}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathscr{D}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathfrak{D}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

中的线性运算关于收敛概念是连续的.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
称
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \varphi_{j}\right\} \subset D$
\end_inset

为Cauchy列, 如果满足
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
存在紧集
\begin_inset Formula $K$
\end_inset

使得
\begin_inset Formula $\text{spt}$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\left(\varphi_{j}\right)\subset K$
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset Formula $j=1,2,\cdots$
\end_inset

);
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
对
\begin_inset Formula $\forall\varepsilon>0$
\end_inset

, 及多重指标
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

, 存在自然数
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

, 使当
\begin_inset Formula $j_{1},j_{2}\ge N$
\end_inset

时有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\max_{x\in K}\left|D^{p}\varphi_{j_{1}}\left(x\right)-D^{p}\varphi_{j_{2}}\left(x\right)\right|<\varepsilon.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

是完备的, 即若
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \varphi_{j}\right\} \subset D$
\end_inset

是任意一个Cauchy列, 则存在
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi\in D$
\end_inset

, 使得
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi_{j}\to\varphi$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

上的一切连续线性泛函, 称为广义函数, 即
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

上的广义函数
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

满足
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
线性: 对任何
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha,\beta$
\end_inset

及
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi_{1},\varphi_{2}\in D$
\end_inset

有
\begin_inset Formula $f\left(\alpha\varphi_{1}+\beta\varphi_{2}\right)=\alpha f\left(\varphi_{1}\right)+\beta f\left(\varphi_{2}\right)$
\end_inset

;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
连续: 设
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \varphi_{j}\right\} \subset D$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi\in D$
\end_inset

, 若
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi_{j}\to\varphi$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

, 则有
\begin_inset Formula $f\left(\varphi_{j}\right)\to f\left(\varphi\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $j\to\infty$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
一切广义函数所组成的集合, 记作
\begin_inset Formula $D'$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
每个
\begin_inset Formula $f\in L_{loc}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

都对应一个函数型广义函数
\begin_inset Formula $f^{*}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $f^{*}\left(\varphi\right)=\int_{\Omega}f\left(x\right)\varphi\left(x\right)\ud x$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\forall\varphi\in D$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
映射
\begin_inset Formula $T:L_{loc}\left(\Omega\right)\to D'$
\end_inset

定义为
\begin_inset Formula $T\left(f\right)=f^{*}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $f^{*}$
\end_inset

定义如上, 则
\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

是一对一线性映射.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
证明较繁?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset Formula $f\in D'$
\end_inset

当且仅当对任意紧集
\begin_inset Formula $K\subset\Omega$
\end_inset

, 存在常数
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

及非负整数
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

, 使得当
\begin_inset Formula $\text{spt}\varphi\subset K$
\end_inset

时有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left|f\left(\varphi\right)\right|\le C\sum_{\left|p\right|\le m}\sup_{x\in K}\left|D^{p}\varphi\right|,\qquad\forall\varphi\in D.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
试证必要性.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
设
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ f_{j}\right\} \subset D'$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $f\in D'$
\end_inset

, 如果对一切
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi\in D$
\end_inset

成立
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lim_{j\to\infty}f_{j}\left(\varphi\right)=f\left(\varphi\right),
\]

\end_inset

则称
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ f_{j}\right\} $
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $D'$
\end_inset

中收敛于
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

, 记为
\begin_inset Formula $f_{j}\to f$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $D'$
\end_inset

.
 
\begin_inset Formula $D'$
\end_inset

按照这种收敛概念, 称为广义函数空间.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
函数型广义函数在
\begin_inset Formula $D'$
\end_inset

中稠密吗?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对任一多重指标
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $D^{p}$
\end_inset

是一个由
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

到
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

的连续线性映射.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proposition
设
\begin_inset Formula $f\in D'$
\end_inset

, 定义
\begin_inset Formula $g\left(\varphi\right)=-f\left(\frac{\partial\varphi}{\partial x_{1}}\right)$
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi\in D$
\end_inset

), 则
\begin_inset Formula $g\in D'$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
\begin_inset Formula $f\in D'$
\end_inset

定义
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

对
\begin_inset Formula $x_{1}$
\end_inset

的一阶偏导数为
\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

, 并记为
\begin_inset Formula $g=\frac{\partial f}{\p x_{1}}$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

仍然是广义函数.
 一般地对任意多重指标
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

, 定义
\begin_inset Formula $D^{p}f$
\end_inset

为如下广义函数:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
g_{p}\left(\varphi\right)=\left(-1\right)^{\left|p\right|}f\left(D^{p}\varphi\right),
\]

\end_inset

即
\begin_inset Formula $D^{p}f=g_{p}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
广义函数可以进行无限次求导运算.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
设
\begin_inset Formula $\Psi\in C^{\infty}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $f\in D'$
\end_inset

, 定义
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

上的泛函为
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\Psi f\right)\left(\varphi\right)=f\left(\Psi\varphi\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi\in D$
\end_inset

, 那么
\begin_inset Formula $\Psi f$
\end_inset

显然是
\begin_inset Formula $D'$
\end_inset

上连续线性泛函, 即
\begin_inset Formula $\Psi f\in D'$
\end_inset

, 称
\begin_inset Formula $\Psi$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $D'$
\end_inset

的一个乘子.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对于
\begin_inset Formula $\Psi\in C^{\infty}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $f\in D'$
\end_inset

, 可定义乘积
\begin_inset Formula $\Psi f$
\end_inset

, 但对于两个一般的广义函数不能定义乘积.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proposition
证明:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
设
\begin_inset Formula $f,g\in D'$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha,\beta$
\end_inset

是数, 则
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\p}{\p x_{j}}\left(\alpha f+\beta g\right)=\alpha\frac{\p f}{\p x_{j}}+\beta\frac{\p g}{\p x_{j}}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $j=1,2,\cdots,n$
\end_inset

;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
设
\begin_inset Formula $\Psi\in C^{\infty}\left(\Omega\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $f\in D'$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\p}{\p x_{j}}\left(\Psi f\right)=\Psi\frac{\p f}{\p x_{j}}+f\frac{\p\Psi}{\p x_{j}}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $j=1,2,\cdots,n$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
设
\begin_inset Formula $f_{j}\in D'$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $f\in D'$
\end_inset

, 若
\begin_inset Formula $f_{j}\to f$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $D'$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\p f_{j}}{\p x_{i}}\to\frac{\p f}{\p x_{i}}$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $D'$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $i=1,2,\cdots,n$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
设
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ f_{j}\right\} \subset D'$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $f\in D'$
\end_inset

, 称级数
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{j=1}^{\infty}f_{j}$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $D'$
\end_inset

中收敛于
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

, 是指前
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

项和
\begin_inset Formula $S_{m}=\sum_{j=1}^{m}f_{j}$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $D'$
\end_inset

中收敛于
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

, 记为
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{j=1}^{\infty}f_{j}=f$
\end_inset

.
 若级数
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{j=1}^{\infty}f_{j}$
\end_inset

收敛于
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

, 则级数
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{j=1}^{\infty}\frac{\p f_{j}}{\p x_{i}}$
\end_inset

收敛于
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\p f}{\p x_{i}}$
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset Formula $i=1,2,\cdots,n$
\end_inset

).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
设
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ f_{j}\right\} \subset D'$
\end_inset

, 如果对每个
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi\in D$
\end_inset

, 极限
\begin_inset Formula $\lim_{j\to\infty}f_{j}\left(\varphi\right)$
\end_inset

存在且有限, 则必存在
\begin_inset Formula $f\in D'$
\end_inset

, 使得
\begin_inset Formula $f_{j}\to f$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $D'$
\end_inset

.
 (要用到拓扑线性空间的知识?)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{\pi}\frac{\sin jx}{x}\to\delta\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $D'$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
